oportional to the temperature, be they positive (repulsive) or negative\n(attractive) in different cases. Our study may be helpful in providing a\ncomprehensive and complete understanding of this old problem.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 17 Feb 2014 08:11:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-18"}
